+  (overline{B_n}, overline{C_n}) -> overline{C_n}
+  (overline{A_n}, overline{C_n}) -> overline{D_n}
+  (overline{D_n}, overline{D_n}) -> overline{A_{n+1}}
+  ```
+
+  together with any mixed mirror companions admitted by the closure rule
